data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER BRING ALL OFFERS! REDUCED!!Take a look at this cute & affordable 3/2/2 on just under half an acre just outside the city limits of Gatesville! You'll love this 1,820 sqft split floor plan that offers ample bedroom space, lots of closets and a nice big open kitchen, dining & living area.  The corner wood burning fireplace is a beautiful & useful bonus! The Master offers a big walk in closet and nice master bath with dual vanities a separate shower and deep faux marble soaking tub! The enclosed back patio makes a great bonus hobby room or sun porch! The oversized lot provides a fenced back yard with 2 nice big storage buildings (1 offers electric & window unit) as well as a beautiful lawn outside the fence. Beautiful mature landscaping & curb appeal! Disclaimer: All room measurements, taxes, and utility info are approx and should be verified by buyer.  Age provided by CCAD.  Square Footage provided by appraisal from previous purchase.
